      &lt;img alt="A photo of the American flag with graphic warning symbols." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/cejMfcN8npjCW5cu6ILNpM5dtDo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73719383/STK432_Government__CVirginia_D.0.jpg" /&gt;
